categories: Category:Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club

nodes.text: Visit to Rancho Obi-Wan was a feature released on the Hyperspace fan club website. It featured a video tour of collector Stephen J. Sansweet's personal museum and various related memorabilia. There were six videos available on the website.
Steve Sansweet is the former Head of Fan Relations and Director of Content Management at Lucasfilm. He is currently the Fan Relations Adviser to Lucasfilm.
